{"tid":526501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"剪香港身份證　前港超內地球員：沒拿香港身份　這輩子最正確的決定","createTime":"2018-01-11T16:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T04:50:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":383,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"732786c428a900e3f14c87eaa5b9fbeb8e91c80d","tid":526501,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/laui23_w6pNF_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flaui23_w6pNF_1200x0.png&h=3c11d296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自內地的前港超聯賽球員劉松偉，繼批評港隊及港隊教練金判坤之後，在Instagram上載一張剪爛的香港身份證、往來港澳通行證的相片，並寫上「一群不懂足球又要發洩的可憐球迷 慢慢吠吧 沒拿香港身份是這輩子做的最正確的決定 沒有之一」，結果引起不少香港網民留言辱罵。<br />\n<br />\n劉松偉早前在中國隊擊敗韓國隊後於Instagram留言，問「你香港要過多少年才做到」，又說港隊教練金判坤「只配給後人留笑話」，以「中國牛逼！香港傻逼！」作結，結果惹來過百名網民辱罵，事件再次被牽扯到中港矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n今年28歲的後衛劉松偉，效力流浪足球會多年，上年在「標準流浪」球風勇悍，表現令人印像深刻。但現時流浪足球會的足總網站專頁上，擁有球衣號碼的大軍名單上，已不見劉松偉的名字。<br />\n<br />\n早前有香港足球代表隊成員白鶴宣佈退出港隊，更表示不會歸隊，直到「香港代表隊不再由（韓國人金教練）帶領為止」，他事後解釋是「尊重」問題，「不存在政治」。"},{"pid":"48998fc0b6c7cd3a310c43d15e36112870260e4a","tid":526501,"uid":159163,"like":99,"dislike":3,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"打假波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d6bb57d54fa6d11d4fcce6089a8ab2c9fc8989","tid":526501,"uid":60787,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cea3ead35141adcf6efe5eb3c7a60e4939aa99","tid":526501,"uid":3457,"like":390,"dislike":4,"score":386,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"剪身分證唔係犯法既咩"},{"pid":"ab1c1153400c4acfee6e1ca98f12fa98645e69a8","tid":526501,"uid":96497,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"支那人翻乜鬼牆 繼續玩微博啦屌"},{"pid":"414275543435de7dfa2c3e2d9709ba9145a422ba","tid":526501,"uid":4519,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:20:29.000Z","msg":"剪左都可以補領<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c724f7cff72bc5d5e49e085cfd40fc41180d08c5","tid":526501,"uid":125006,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"其實可以補領"},{"pid":"13d9b8ceb2b5f817e219639c8ebd585a8fc9a740","tid":526501,"uid":5195,"like":339,"dislike":2,"score":337,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"之後劉松偉向球員表示有人須為事件負責，要黃及其他球員交出一萬元，而李亦因未能操縱比賽而感害怕。有球員之後亦表示他們須接受外圍莊家指示操縱賽事賽果，以達到外國莊家要求便可收錢，否則便要賠償。李在警誡下承認劉曾給予指示。<span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，劉松偉現時被通緝。</span>"},{"pid":"56eb9f2c399e279f39c63de9c50d9d1ac8d5c7b8","tid":526501,"uid":88123,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"邊個亂發身份證比d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw邊鬼個嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071bd214fbfec07ee0eaf75ac4662f2e4a239a81","tid":526501,"uid":79563,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">來自內地</span></span>的前港超聯賽球員劉松偉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原本就係蝗蟲！"},{"pid":"bf70d6614697a3319116ec18e99e16b0df1e0f99","tid":526501,"uid":54264,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"剪爛左可以再申請返扮咩野姐"},{"pid":"734c42cfa6eaba87670c6bbf4c1a08d5d4946533","tid":526501,"uid":23815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"56eb9f2c399e279f39c63de9c50d9d1ac8d5c7b8","tid":526501,"uid":88123,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"邊個亂發身份證比d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw邊鬼個嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"一粒星work visa都要比架"},{"pid